---
title: HelloHero: Double Satay Chicken & Veggie Curry with Rapid Rice & Broccoli
description: A satay chicken curry, it has our hearts fluttering and our mouths watering as the hearty curry aromas sweep the kitchen. On a bed of fluffy rice, we’re head over heels for this meal!

